Syntax: fleche <target>

Executes a fleche, a running thrust attack drawn from classical fencing
technique. The attacker launches forward in a straight line, delivering a
powerful lunge that is difficult to parry. Fleche is a Warrior-line finisher
skill: it requires a valid finisher combo count before it can be used.

Fleche is available to Warden-class characters and their remort descendants
(Knight, Swordsman, Crusader).

Requirements:
  - Must be in combat.
  - Requires a valid finisher combo count (combo threshold met).
  - Target must be present in the room.
  - Must have the skill learned.

See also: shelp fleche charge riposte holystrike
